OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fmostly dry evening with some late
OL,7,Fbrightness. Clear spells will develop
OL,8,Fovernight but becoming cloudier with
OL,9,Fsome showers across the far north
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA mostly dry morning with
OL,13,Fsunny spells but some showers in the
OL,14,Ffar north. Turning cloudy in the
OL,15,Fafternoon with showers becoming
OL,16,Fwidespread. Feeling cool with fresh
OL,17,Fwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
