OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,6,Fmixture of sunshine and blustery
OL,7,Fshowers on Tuesday and Wednesday, the
OL,8,Fshowers wintry on the hills. Some rain
OL,9,Fpossible on Thursday. Feeling cold for
OL,10,Fthe time of year.
